CloudFactory,is,a,service,that,allows,businesses,and,developers,to,integrate,a,virtual,factory,for,all,types,of,digital,work,such,as,tagging,images,moderating,content,generating,sales,leads,and,transcribing,audio,content,The,work,is,done,virtually,by,workers,around,the,world,The,CloudFactory,API,is,what,allows,developers,to,integrate,jobs,and,work,into,other,applications,and,sites,Some,example,API,methods,include,accessing,jobs,and,status,of,jobs,account,information,worker,information,and,adding,and,editing,job,and,account,information